window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Less than 24 hours ago, I'd&nbsp;stood right here, wearing that dress, telling a boy I loved him.</p> <p>Oh, how the mighty fell.</p> <p>They betrayed me.</p> <p>Three boys I thought I knew.</p> <p>Leaving me with the one I thought I hated most.</p> <p>It was him who carried my broken, beaten body. Him who cleaned my wounds and held me tight.</p> <p>The prince to my princess.</p> <p>Lies.</p> <p>I won’t be that girl anymore. The one who fell for their smooth words and smoldering looks.</p> <p>Colt is key to never being her again.</p> <p>There’s still a killer on the loose.</p> <p>Still a murder left unsolved.</p> <p>Still three boys who own my heart.</p> <p>But some dangerous little secrets are better left buried.</p> <p>His is one of them.</p> <p><i>Dangerous Little Secrets</i>&nbsp;is the story of three bad boys and a girl who knows how to stand her ground. It is a mature high school/new adult, #whychoose romance, meaning the main character has more than one love interest. This book contains enemies-to-lovers and bullying themes. It is the second book in an ongoing trilogy and cannot be listened to as a stand-alone. Book one is <i>Devious Little Liars</i>.&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Get this hot new romance today.</b></p>"; 
